text: Jürgen Luczak (born 28 November 1943) is a German wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 63 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of East Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Murska Sobota
